room_title: Escape room "Outlaws" by Time Travel Escapes in West Palm Beach
room_description: Sheriff Patterson's Old Western Town is in trouble again. Your team must travel back 20 years later and help them clean up the town. The saloon owner Brody the Bruiser Barrington is a known outlaw that is in the pocket of the sheriff. There have been a string of robberies in the last month and the rumors have it his saloon is the hangout for these criminals. You must discover which outlaw is the gang leader and recover the stolen loot. You and your team must rid the town of these gang members and the master mind behind it all.
